data.description: Updated Craftsman home in beautiful North Muskegon! Offering many amenities, close proximity to Bear & Muskegon Lake, beaches, conservation club, walking trail, multiple boat launch sites, State Parks, Luge Park, hiking trails, shopping centers, taverns, and fine dining. Minutes from downtown Muskegon, easy access to US 31 & business 31. Settled in the North Muskegon School District, offering an attractive and rare price point for the area. Sought-after and surrounded by nature, water, & beauty. Situated on a corner lot, this home boasts 4 bedrooms,1 bath (2 bathroom capable), open main floor plan, a four-seasons front room, and an attached garage. Deck is just off the dining room for easy access and entertaining. The backyard is completely enclosed with a 6ft wrap-around privacy fence.
